### Get User's Ratings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ratings/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Movie Ratings (for specific movie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ratings/movie/movie_1

### Get Another Movie's Ratings
